   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="1907_AS_RBH_1_00041"/>Dr. Richard Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb259" type="place">Venedig Lido</rs></hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="1907_AS_RBH_1_00040"/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs ref="#pmb41086" type="place"><hi rend="capitals">Palast-Hotel</hi></rs></hi></p><p rend="center"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs ref="#pmb43520" type="place"><hi rend="capitals">Meran</hi></rs></hi></p><p rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs ref="#pmb41086" type="place">Palast-Hotel, Meran</rs></hi><lb/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb51866">Franz Leibl</rs>, Hotelier</hi></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="1907_AS_RBH_1_00041"/><salute>lieber Richard,</salute> ich habe keine Nachricht von Ihnen. In <rs ref="#pmb40260" type="place">Bozen</rs> war nichts (3 Briefe u ein Telegra<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>cheint ein Unberufener abgeholt zu haben) la<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en Sie
               mich ein Wort hören. Nach <rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs>, wo wir (über <rs ref="#pmb40260" type="place">Bozen</rs>, <rs type="place" ref="#pmb41083">Mendel</rs>, Sa<unclear>lzg</unclear>, <rs ref="#pmb867" type="place">I<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>sbruck</rs>, ev. <rs ref="#pmb30" type="place">Salzburg</rs>) Freitag zu<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ein hoffen.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Ihr<lb/><signed>A.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
